data.description: This spacious two-story home has an inviting open floor plan. On the main level you will find an eat-in kitchen with a breakfast bar, main living area, full bathroom and an office/playroom.  Upstairs offers a large loft area, three bedrooms and two full bathrooms.  Escape the heat with a gorgeous backyard swimming pool with water features.  Conveniently located close to schools, shopping, golf courses, parks and freeway access.  AC, roof, pool pump, and water heater were all replaced within the past five years.
